## 8. Maintenance and housekeeping

- **When behavior changes**, update **§3** and the relevant `docs/` or `_reference/plans/` entry—not durable principles unless values changed.
- **Agent rules:** Some `.agents/rules/*.mdc` files may lag renames. Prefer **README** and **AGENTS** when they disagree with older rules until those files are updated.
- **Single source of truth:** This rule summarizes; if a detail conflicts with `docs/` or `README`, **trust the dedicated doc** and update this index. Canonical long-form copy: [_reference/aero-principles-and-goals.md](_reference/aero-principles-and-goals.md).

